param.string: CASE WHEN @subStr($Aggregation.mvyt24be_rubrica, 0, 2) = 'P' THEN 'liability' WHEN @subStr($Aggregation.mvyt24be_rubrica, 0, 2) = 'A' THEN 'asset' WHEN @subStr($Aggregation.mvyt24be_rubrica, 0, 2) = 'O' THEN 'memo' WHEN @subStr($Aggregation.mvyt24be_rubrica, 0, 2) = 'N' THEN 'capital' WHEN @subStr($Aggregation.mvyt24be_rubrica, 0, 2) = 'R' THEN 'capital'  ELSE 'na' END

CASE WHEN $Aggregation.mvyt24be_rubrica IN ('A04020501','A04040501','A05030201','A05030301','A050401','A050601') THEN 'yes' 	WHEN @subStr($Aggregation.mvyt24be_rubrica, 0, 5) = 'P0802' THEN 'yes' 	WHEN @subStr($Aggregation.mvyt24be_rubrica, 0, 5) = 'P0804' THEN 'yes' 	ELSE 'no' END
